msgid "maxframe.tensor.atleast\\_2d"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d:1 of
msgid "View inputs as tensors with at least two dimensions."
msgstr "将输入视为至少二维的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d:3
#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d:7
#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d:11 of
msgid ""
"One or more array-like sequences.  Non-tensor inputs are converted to "
"tensors.  Tensors that already have two or more dimensions are preserved."
msgstr ""
"一个或多个类数组序列。非张量输入会被转换为张量。已经具有两个或更多维度的"
"张量会被保留。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_2d.atleast_2d:16 of
msgid ""
"**res, res2, ...** -- A tensor, or list of tensors, each with ``a.ndim >="
" 2``. Copies are avoided where possible, and views with two or more "
"dimensions are returned."
msgstr ""
"**res, res2, ...** -- 一个张量，或张量列表，每个张量都满足 ``a.ndim >= 2`"
"`。尽可能避免复制，返回具有两个或更多维度的视图。"

